product_name: Ahnu Tilden IV Water Shoes - Women's
long_description: The women's Ahnu Tilden IV Water Shoes are built on the lightweight, stable Ahnu Traverse Platform so you can go all day in the water or on a trail and feel secure and protected. Lightweight dual-density EVA midsoles and footbeds provide comfort and shock absorption. Quick-dry mesh uppers feature integrated webbing for snug fit. Thermoplastic urethane heel straps ensure secure heel positioning. Lateral-to-medial heel clips create neutral foot positioning.
